{"article_id":"N2b3rD9t52AucyYP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"All five senators","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"considered to be swing votes against Kavanaugh","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"have now apparently made up their minds .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"And enough of them have said","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"they support him","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"that his nomination will likely pass .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"By late in the week , all eyes were on Republican Sens . Jeff Flake , Lisa Murkowski and Susan Collins , as well as Democratic Sens . Heidi Heitkamp and Joe Manchin .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"Given Republicans ' razor-thin 51-49 majority in the Senate ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"their collective votes would likely be the deciding factor","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"in whether or not Kavanaugh is ultimately confirmed to the Supreme Court .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"As of Friday afternoon , all five of them have now indicated how they ' d vote :","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"Heitkamp will oppose Kavanaugh","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"and Murkowski appears likely to do so as well ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"while Flake , Collins and Manchin have signaled","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"that they will vote in favor .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Susan Collins :","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"Collins announced in a Friday afternoon floor speech","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"that she will be supporting Kavanaugh .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"She had signaled as much on Thursday","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"when she expressed confidence in the FBI report on sexual misconduct allegations against Kavanaugh .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"\" It appears to be a very thorough investigation ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"but I ' m going back later","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"to personally read the interviews , \"","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"Collins told reporters about the FBI report on Thursday .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Later in the day , Collins reiterated the sentiment ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"noting","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"\" I ' ve not yet finished going through all the materials , \"","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"according to CNN ' s Manu Raju .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"Jeff Flake :","depth":4},{"id":29,"text":"Flake said on Friday","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"that he intends to vote in support of Kavanaugh","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"unless things change ahead of a floor vote .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"He told reporters","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"it was a tough decision ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"according to NBC News ' Alex Moe .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"Flake also echoed Collins in his reaction toward the FBI report .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"\" I think","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"Susan Collins was quoted","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"saying","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"it was very thorough","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"but no new corroborative information came out of it .","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"That ' s accurate , \"","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Flake told reporters at the Capitol on Thursday .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"\" I wanted this pause ;","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"we ' ve had this pause .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"We ' ve had the professionals , the FBI , determine","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"- given the scope","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"that we gave them , current credible allegations -","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"to go and do their review ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"which they ' ve done. \"","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Flake was at the forefront of calls for a one-week delay on a Kavanaugh vote ,","depth":4},{"id":51,"text":"which would enable the FBI to conduct an investigation .","depth":4},{"id":52,"text":"He voted in favor","depth":4},{"id":53,"text":"of limiting debate on the nomination","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"and advancing Kavanaugh to a floor vote on Friday .","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"Lisa Murkowski :","depth":4},{"id":56,"text":"In a surprising turn , Murkowski voted against limiting debate on the nomination","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"and advancing Kavanaugh to a floor vote on Friday .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"This vote is likely indicative of how she ultimately plans to vote on Kavanaugh .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"She appeared to spell this out more plainly to reporters after the vote .","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"\" I believe","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Brett Kavanaugh is a good man , \"","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"she said .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"\" It just may be that in my view he ' s not the right man for the court at this time . \"","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"Previously , Murkowski had held her cards a bit closer to the chest ,","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"noting","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"that she was still working on reading the entirety of the FBI report herself .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"\" I ' m not wasting any daylight here , \"","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"she said on Thursday .","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"She did add , however ,","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"that she agreed with an assessment","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"Collins had previously made","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"that Kavanaugh was not likely to overturn Roe v. Wade .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":145,"left":122,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":87,"right":121,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":78,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":75,"right":77,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":74,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":74,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":76,"right":5,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":86,"left":81,"right":85,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":81,"